      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/02/sriranga-gadhyam/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;SrI: SrImathE SatakOpAya nama: SrImathE rAmAnujAya nama: SrImath varavaramunayE nama:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/periyaperumal-art.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/periyaperumal-art.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/periyaperumal-art.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;periyaperumal-art&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sriman-narayanan/&#34;&gt;SrIrangaAthan&lt;/a&gt; – mUlavar and uthsavar – SrIrangam&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ramanuja-srirangam.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ramanuja-srirangam.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ramanuja-srirangam.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;ramanuja-srirangam&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/emperumanar/&#34;&gt;SrI rAmAnuja&lt;/a&gt; – SrIrangam&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/periyavachan-pillai.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/periyavachan-pillai.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/periyavachan-pillai.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;periyavachan-pillai&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/periyavachchan-pillai/&#34;&gt;periyavAchchAn piLLai&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;e-book – &lt;a href=&#34;https://1drv.ms/b/s!AiNzc-LF3uwyggcC27ss2yHu_CQf&#34;&gt;https://1drv.ms/b/s!AiNzc-LF3uwyggcC27ss2yHu_CQf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;After &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2015/11/saranagathi-gadhyam/&#34;&gt;SaraNAgathi gadhyam&lt;/a&gt;, bhagavath rAmAnuja continues to recite SrIranga gadhyam in glorification of SrIranganAthan who is the presiding deity of SrIrangam. Let us enjoy this treatise now.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/02/sriranga-gadhyam-thaniyan/&#34;&gt;thaniyan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/02/sriranga-gadhyam-pravesam/&#34;&gt;pravESam&#xA;(Introduction)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;chUrNai 1&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/02/sriranga-gadhyam-1-part-1/&#34;&gt;Part&#xA;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/03/sriranga-gadhyam-1-part-2/&#34;&gt;Part&#xA;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/03/sriranga-gadhyam-2/&#34;&gt;chUrNai&#xA;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/03/sriranga-gadhyam-3/&#34;&gt;chUrNai&#xA;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/03/sriranga-gadhyam-4-5/&#34;&gt;chUrNais 4 and&#xA;5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/03/sriranga-gadhyam-6/&#34;&gt;chUrNai&#xA;6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/03/sriranga-gadhyam-7/&#34;&gt;chUrNai&#xA;7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;saranagathi-gadhyam&#34;&gt;SaraNAgathi gadhyam&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;SrI: SrImathE satakOpAya nama: SrImathE rAmAnujAya nama: SrImath varavaramunayE nama:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
